#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ellipk.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.ellipk"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:1 of
msgid "Complete elliptic integral of the first kind."
msgstr "第一类完全椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:3 of
msgid "This function is defined as"
msgstr "该函数定义为"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:5 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"K(m) = \\int_0^{\\pi/2} [1 - m \\sin(t)^2]^{-1/2} dt\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ellipk.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:7 of
msgid "The parameter of the elliptic integral."
msgstr "椭圆积分的参数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:9 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function values"
msgstr "函数值的可选输出数组"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ellipk.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:12 of
msgid "**K** -- Value of the elliptic integral."
msgstr "**K** —— 椭圆积分的值。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.ellipk.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:17 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ellipkm1`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:18 of
msgid "Complete elliptic integral of the first kind around m = 1"
msgstr "在 m = 1 附近的第一类完全椭圆积分"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:20 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ellipkinc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:21 of
msgid "Incomplete elliptic integral of the first kind"
msgstr "第一类不完全椭圆积分"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:23 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ellipe`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:24 of
msgid "Complete elliptic integral of the second kind"
msgstr "第二类完全椭圆积分"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:26 of
msgid ":py:obj:`ellipeinc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:27 of
msgid "Incomplete elliptic integral of the second kind"
msgstr "第二类不完全椭圆积分"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`elliprf`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:30 of
msgid "Completely-symmetric elliptic integral of the first kind."
msgstr "第一类完全对称椭圆积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:33 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:34 of
msgid ""
"For more precision around point m = 1, use `ellipkm1`, which this "
"function calls."
msgstr "为了在 m = 1 附近获得更高的精度，请使用此函数所调用的 `ellipkm1`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:37 of
msgid ""
"The parameterization in terms of :math:`m` follows that of section 17.2 "
"in [1]_. Other parameterizations in terms of the complementary parameter "
":math:`1 - m`, modular angle :math:`\\sin^2(\\alpha) = m`, or modulus "
":math:`k^2 = m` are also used, so be careful that you choose the correct "
"parameter."
msgstr ""
"以 :math:`m` 为参数的形式遵循 [1]_ 第 17.2 节中的定义。其他参数化方式包括"
"互补参数 :math:`1 - m`、模角 :math:`\\sin^2(\\alpha) = m` 或模数 :math:`k"
"^2 = m` 也被使用，因此请确保选择正确的参数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:43 of
msgid ""
"The Legendre K integral is related to Carlson's symmetric R_F function by"
" [2]_:"
msgstr "Legendre K 积分与 Carlson 的对称 R_F 函数的关系由 [2]_ 给出："

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:46 of
msgid ""
"K(m) = R_F(0, 1-k^2, 1) .\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:49 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:50 of
msgid ""
"Milton Abramowitz and Irene A. Stegun, eds. Handbook of Mathematical "
"Functions with Formulas, Graphs, and Mathematical Tables. New York: "
"Dover, 1972."
msgstr ""
"Milton Abramowitz 和 Irene A. Stegun 编。数学函数手册：公式、图表与数学表"
"。纽约：Dover，1972 年。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.ellip_func_integrals.ellipk:53 of
msgid ""
"NIST Digital Library of Mathematical Functions. http://dlmf.nist.gov/, "
"Release 1.0.28 of 2020-09-15. See Sec. 19.25(i) "
"https://dlmf.nist.gov/19.25#i"
msgstr ""
"NIST 数学函数数字图书馆。http://dlmf.nist.gov/，2020-09-15 的 1.0.28 版。"
"参见第 19.25(i) 节 https://dlmf.nist.gov/19.25#i"

